膠彈<br />\n19. 銅鑼灣 對被捕示威者插贓嫁禍<br />\n20. 銅鑼灣 警察扮示威者射丫叉 混入人群搞事後表露身分制服旁人同時大量防暴增援<br />\n21. 全港 蓄意傷害無反抗能力之人士 有示威者被打至血流披面 門牙飛脫"},{"pid":"5a13881b7cecc0e0899e3112fdd8e96231ca5cd8","tid":1451562,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:40:31.000Z","msg":"邊撚個負皮我"},{"pid":"66a4349e4639c82a6f85d81c8245749f24645431","tid":1451562,"uid":304936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:44:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28e5b094a5c046e42ca814a48785ca6bcf359356","tid":1451562,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:58:28.000Z","msg":"國家恐怖主義 <br />\nState Terrorism<br />\n國家對平民進行恐怖襲擊"},{"pid":"f2472e7d5e059ecff02e5770da62f6d1175797b8","tid":1451562,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:03:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"30086e2fed94d22a1f48fe818ec584cecdf28104","tid":1451562,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:35:00.000Z","msg":"Stare Terrorism"},{"pid":"548cd213c1707ed1b26e1f3c5f41192be1fded27","tid":1451562,"uid":19619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:41:21.000Z","msg":"Posh"},{"pid":"e2034ee54debf78a3806fd5ac508f164fd764a5d","tid":1451562,"uid":168188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:42:58.000Z","msg":"[英文]文宣整合! 幫手印/分享上social media<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451736</a>"},{"pid":"efb30d4d0a1083da39a80f57b0a5cdd7dbdf3a13","tid":1451562,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:51:01.000Z","msg":"國家對市民恐怖襲擊"},{"pid":"e9f2429374ed12f71a38eee6187d033bdeb1dd17","tid":1451562,"uid":24875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:52:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明一次過包埋屌政府點解唔落重鎚"}]}